sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as POST /api/v1/upload
    participant Manager as GuestSessionManager
    participant DB as guest_sessions
    participant Pipeline as OCR / AI pipeline

    Client->>API: Upload file + X-Guest-Session-Id
    API->>Manager: can_use(UPLOAD)
    Manager->>DB: Check upload_count less than GUEST_UPLOAD_LIMIT
    alt upload_count already 1
        DB-->>Manager: limit reached
        Manager-->>API: GuestLimitExceeded 403
    else under limit
        DB-->>Manager: OK
        API->>API: Validate file, create MedicalCase
        API->>Pipeline: Enqueue processing
        API->>Manager: increment_upload (after success)
        Manager->>DB: Atomic UPDATE upload_count + 1 WHERE upload_count less than 1
        DB-->>Client: 201 case_id + lab_result
        Note over Client,DB: Second upload on same session returns 403
    end
